in-laws, the man, your parents

00:16:42.750 --> 00:16:43.550 align:middle line:90%
just tell you?

00:16:43.550 --> 00:16:44.370 align:middle line:90%
How does a proposal happen?

00:16:44.370 --> 00:16:47.150 align:middle line:84%
>>SONI: So the proposal comes is
that everybody in the community

00:16:47.150 --> 00:16:49.530 align:middle line:84%
knows when you are
at a certain age.

00:16:49.530 --> 00:16:51.050 align:middle line:84%
I mean, starting
from 16, everybody

00:16:51.050 --> 00:16:53.240 align:middle line:84%
is keeping an eye on you
because you are like--

00:16:53.240 --> 00:16:55.615 align:middle line:84%
and you can't go too far
because, otherwise, you're going

00:16:55.615 --> 00:16:57.140 align:middle line:90%
to be an old maid pretty fast.

00:16:57.140 --> 00:17:00.110 align:middle line:84%
And the only reason I was able
to dodge the bullet up to 21

00:17:00.110 --> 00:17:01.770 align:middle line:84%
is because I was
a valedictorian.

00:17:01.770 --> 00:17:03.598 align:middle line:84%
I was very serious
about my education.

00:17:03.598 --> 00:17:05.640 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise, I would have
been married before that.

00:17:05.640 --> 00:17:06.560 align:middle line:90%
So I'm 21.

00:17:06.560 --> 00:17:08.750 align:middle line:84%
And basically, I
get seen by this.

00:17:08.750 --> 00:17:13.550 align:middle line:84%
And then they come to the house,
for example, the mutual party,

00:17:13.550 --> 00:17:16.130 align:middle line:84%
my cousin would come
to my dad and mom

00:17:16.130 --> 00:17:17.810 align:middle line:84%
and say, you know
what, we really see

00:17:17.810 --> 00:17:19.440 align:middle line:90%
a very good proposal for her.

00:17:19.440 --> 00:17:20.670 align:middle line:90%
It looks really good.

00:17:20.670 --> 00:17:22.020 align:middle line:90%
Everything checks off.

00:17:22.020 --> 00:17:24.660 align:middle line:84%
How about we create a meeting
for all of them to meet?

00:17:24.660 --> 00:17:26.015 align:middle line:90%
And that's how it works.

00:17:26.015 --> 00:17:28.387 align:middle line:84%
And that same party goes to
the other party and says,

00:17:28.387 --> 00:17:30.470 align:middle line:84%
I have this girl I think
that he's going to like--

00:17:30.470 --> 00:17:32.790 align:middle line:90%
So they choreograph all of that.

00:17:32.790 --> 00:17:36.100 align:middle line:90%
And he had seven girls lined up.

00:17:36.100 --> 00:17:37.580 align:middle line:90%
I was the fifth girl.

00:17:37.580 --> 00:17:38.630 align:middle line:90%
I was the fifth girl.

00:17:38.630 --> 00:17:41.480 align:middle line:84%
And then we are basically--
we are only given one hour.

00:17:41.480 --> 00:17:43.073 align:middle line:84%
So basically, we
are giving one hour.

00:17:43.073 --> 00:17:44.740 align:middle line:84%
Can you believe it's
about the same time

00:17:44.740 --> 00:17:47.440 align:middle line:84%
you and I are going to have
and you decide your entire life

00:17:47.440 --> 00:17:48.520 align:middle line:90%
script?

00:17:48.520 --> 00:17:49.090 align:middle line:90%
Can you believe that?

00:17:49.090 --> 00:17:49.860 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: In an hour.

00:17:49.860 --> 00:17:50.225 align:middle line:90%
Wow.

00:17:50.225 --> 00:17:52.630 align:middle line:84%
>>SONI: And then in that one
hour, he actually interviewed.

00:17:52.630 --> 00:17:53.780 align:middle line:84%
And he asked me
all the questions.

00:17:53.780 --> 00:17:55.300 align:middle line:84%
He said, do you
know how to cook?

00:17:55.300 --> 00:17:56.118 align:middle line:90%
And I said, no.

00:17:56.118 --> 00:17:57.410 align:middle line:90%
He said, can you speak English?

00:17:57.410 --> 00:17:58.210 align:middle line:90%
I said, no.

00:17:58.210 --> 00:18:00.940 align:middle line:84%
So he was asking and I was--
and he was like completely

00:18:00.940 --> 00:18:04.820 align:middle line:84%
taken by my honesty because
he can see that, oh my God,

00:18:04.820 --> 00:18:06.650 align:middle line:84%
she's really not
even saying yeah.

00:18:06.650 --> 00:18:09.535 align:middle line:84%
And then I said, I can make
a tea and I can make rice.

00:18:09.535 --> 00:18:10.870 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:18:10.870 --> 00:18:12.110 align:middle line:90%
So I was very honest about--

00:18:12.110 --> 00:18:13.575 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: I can keep us alive.

00:18:13.575 --> 00:18:15.040 align:middle line:90%
>>SONI: And then I said that--

00:18:15.040 --> 00:18:16.560 align:middle line:84%
when he said, do
you speak English?

00:18:16.560 --> 00:18:19.060 align:middle line:84%
I said, I can tell you Newton's
first, second, and third law

00:18:19.060 --> 00:18:21.490 align:middle line:84%
of motion in English
because science was still

00:18:21.490 --> 00:18:23.260 align:middle line:90%
taught in English.

00:18:23.260 --> 00:18:25.100 align:middle line:84%
So I was very honest
about everything.

00:18:25.100 --> 00:18:26.870 align:middle line:90%
And I think he liked that.

00:18:26.870 --> 00:18:28.600 align:middle line:84%
He was like taken by
the fact-- and then

00:18:28.600 --> 00:18:30.680 align:middle line:84%
he knew about me
being a valedictorian.

00:18:30.680 --> 00:18:33.790 align:middle line:84%
So he knew that this
girl has a potential

00:18:33.790 --> 00:18:35.340 align:middle line:84%
to be able to
survive in America,

00:18:35.340 --> 00:18:37.170 align:middle line:84%
even though she
doesn't speak English.

00:18:37.170 --> 00:18:39.240 align:middle line:84%
And then I only ask
him one question.

00:18:39.240 --> 00:18:41.210 align:middle line:84%
I said, will I be
able to continue

00:18:41.210 --> 00:18:43.670 align:middle line:90%
my education after marriage?

00:18:43.670 --> 00:18:45.130 align:middle line:90%
And he said, yes, of course.

00:18:45.130 --> 00:18:45.937 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Bingo.

00:18:45.937 --> 00:18:46.770 align:middle line:90%
>>SONI: That was it.

00:18:46.770 --> 00:18:47.687 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That was it.

00:18:47.687 --> 00:18:50.540 align:middle line:84%
Now, meanwhile, you were not
dating around during this time

00:18:50.540 --> 00:18:52.940 align:middle line:84%
because you knew
how the culture was.

00:18:52.940 --> 00:18:54.440 align:middle line:84%
And you did not
want to put yourself

00:18:54.440 --> 00:18:56.630 align:middle line:84%
in a precarious position,
because there's also

00:18:56.630 --> 00:18:57.965 align:middle line:90%
such a thing as honor killing.

00:18:57.965 --> 00:18:58.765 align:middle line:90%
>>SONI: 100%.

00:18:58.765 --> 00:19:00.410 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:19:00.410 --> 00:19:02.870 align:middle line:84%
Please share with us what
honor killing was all about

00:19:02.870 --> 00:19:05.075 align:middle line:84%
and why you didn't
choose to date.

00:19:05.075 --> 00:19:05.875 align:middle line:90%
Smart girl.

00:19:05.875 --> 00:19:09.530 align:middle line:84%
>>SONI: Honor killing generally,
which is such a wrong way

00:19:09.530 --> 00:19:12.830 align:middle line:84%
to even sell that perception,
if you think about it, where men

00:19:12.830 --> 00:19:17.630 align:middle line:84%
uses the fact that they can kill
a woman just because supposedly,

00:19:17.630 --> 00:19:20.270 align:middle line:84%
what they are doing,
if they spend a night

00:19:20.270 --> 00:19:23.670 align:middle line:84%
outside of the household,
then they can kill them.

00:19:23.670 --> 00:19:25.280 align:middle line:84%
Even if they were
not raped, even

00:19:25.280 --> 00:19:26.820 align:middle line:84%
if they didn't have
any intercourse,

00:19:26.820 --> 00:19:30.530 align:middle line:84%
at the end of the day, if
they are outside at night

00:19:30.530 --> 00:19:33.900 align:middle line:84%
without the permission of the
man that is in charge of them,

00:19:33.900 --> 00:19:36.140 align:middle line:84%
then they basically feel
like they have a permission

00:19:36.140 --> 00:19:37.990 align:middle line:90%
to kill them for that.

00:19:37.990 --> 00:19:40.400 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I mean, if
you're in your household

00:19:40.400 --> 00:19:44.400 align:middle line:84%
