Is it a spouse?

00:19:52.190 --> 00:19:54.380 align:middle line:84%
If your spouse has
been out all night

00:19:54.380 --> 00:19:57.410 align:middle line:84%
or if they think that you've
maybe fooled around with a boy

00:19:57.410 --> 00:19:59.550 align:middle line:84%
before marriage,
who can kill you?

00:19:59.550 --> 00:20:01.100 align:middle line:84%
>>SONI: So basically,
all the people

00:20:01.100 --> 00:20:04.850 align:middle line:84%
who believe that they represent
the men in your life, so

00:20:04.850 --> 00:20:06.890 align:middle line:84%
all your blood
relatives and especially

00:20:06.890 --> 00:20:10.070 align:middle line:84%
your father, your brother,
your uncle, because you are

00:20:10.070 --> 00:20:12.380 align:middle line:84%
like-- it's like you are a
representation of a respect

00:20:12.380 --> 00:20:13.180 align:middle line:90%
for them.

00:20:13.180 --> 00:20:15.330 align:middle line:84%
And you're supposed to stay
in a certain parameter.

00:20:15.330 --> 00:20:17.000 align:middle line:90%
So if you do anything unknown--

00:20:17.000 --> 00:20:19.640 align:middle line:84%
and then see, it's a
very fear-based culture.

00:20:19.640 --> 00:20:23.080 align:middle line:84%
So they have created this so
nobody can dare fall in love,

00:20:23.080 --> 00:20:25.080 align:middle line:84%
nobody can run away with
the man that they love,

00:20:25.080 --> 00:20:27.920 align:middle line:84%
nobody can do that because
at the end of the day,

00:20:27.920 --> 00:20:29.710 align:middle line:84%
they would beat the
life out of you.

00:20:29.710 --> 00:20:30.510 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:20:30.510 --> 00:20:31.320 align:middle line:90%
You risk your life.

00:20:31.320 --> 00:20:32.720 align:middle line:90%
I mean, it's-- yeah.

00:20:32.720 --> 00:20:35.120 align:middle line:84%
>>SONI: And then they really
usually really mess up

00:20:35.120 --> 00:20:37.070 align:middle line:84%
both of their lives
because both of them

00:20:37.070 --> 00:20:38.810 align:middle line:90%
will be definitely separated.

