00:20:45.410 --> 00:20:47.075 align:middle line:84%
lives through it,
the experience.

00:20:47.075 --> 00:20:47.875 align:middle line:90%
>>SONI: Exactly.

00:20:47.875 --> 00:20:48.675 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:20:48.675 --> 00:20:50.450 align:middle line:84%
So that is the thing
that honor killing--

