so it depends on the
literacy rate of the place.

00:20:53.390 --> 00:20:54.920 align:middle line:84%
So like in villages,
of course, they

00:20:54.920 --> 00:20:56.660 align:middle line:90%
do that more than the cities.

00:20:56.660 --> 00:20:58.520 align:middle line:84%
So if the literacy rate
is a little higher,

00:20:58.520 --> 00:20:59.927 align:middle line:90%
then people are more educated.

00:20:59.927 --> 00:21:01.760 align:middle line:84%
So you would say that
they have a little bit

00:21:01.760 --> 00:21:03.680 align:middle line:90%
more-- consciousness about it.

00:21:03.680 --> 00:21:06.320 align:middle line:84%
So like my father is not
someone who would have done it

00:21:06.320 --> 00:21:07.820 align:middle line:90%
because he was educated.

00:21:07.820 --> 00:21:10.670 align:middle line:84%
And he was very
intellectual in his own way.

00:21:10.670 --> 00:21:14.210 align:middle line:84%
However, I knew that the
culture itself doesn't really

00:21:14.210 --> 00:21:15.230 align:middle line:90%
promote that.

00:21:15.230 --> 00:21:18.020 align:middle line:84%
So if my father doesn't
agree, still my uncle

00:21:18.020 --> 00:21:20.060 align:middle line:84%
can convince him
because the culture

00:21:20.060 --> 00:21:22.200 align:middle line:90%
is all about everybody else.

00:21:22.200 --> 00:21:23.840 align:middle line:90%
It's not one person ever.

00:21:23.840 --> 00:21:26.100 align:middle line:84%
It's always everybody
else making decisions.

00:21:26.100 --> 00:21:28.960 align:middle line:84%
And you're always doing because
you are worried about what

00:21:28.960 --> 00:21:30.210 align:middle line:90%
other people are going to say.

00:21:30.210 --> 00:21:33.170 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So you just
kept your nose clean,

00:21:33.170 --> 00:21:34.680 align:middle line:90%
kept your nose in the books.

00:21:34.680 --> 00:21:35.810 align:middle line:90%
So you get married now.

00:21:35.810 --> 00:21:37.400 align:middle line:84%
And you come to
the United States

00:21:37.400 --> 00:21:39.110 align:middle line:90%
