00:22:19.195 --> 00:22:20.570 align:middle line:84%
They just have to
look beautiful.

00:22:20.570 --> 00:22:23.310 align:middle line:84%
And the rest happens because
the guy is falling for them.

00:22:23.310 --> 00:22:25.190 align:middle line:84%
They're going to do
everything for them.

00:22:25.190 --> 00:22:26.330 align:middle line:90%
So no matter what--

00:22:26.330 --> 00:22:29.070 align:middle line:84%
I mean, who doesn't like
such a nice love story?

00:22:29.070 --> 00:22:30.860 align:middle line:84%
So to some extent,
we're all programmed

00:22:30.860 --> 00:22:33.270 align:middle line:84%
into believing that
when you get married,

00:22:33.270 --> 00:22:35.163 align:middle line:84%
the man is going to be
the love of your life.

00:22:35.163 --> 00:22:37.080 align:middle line:84%
And it's going to be the
most incredible life.

00:22:37.080 --> 00:22:39.450 align:middle line:84%
And I was under that
exact same impression.

00:22:39.450 --> 00:22:41.990 align:middle line:84%
But my entire fairy tale
broke on the wedding

00:22:41.990 --> 00:22:45.655 align:middle line:84%
night when I learned that he
was in love with someone else.

00:22:45.655 --> 00:22:46.530 align:middle line:90%
And then, of course--

00:22:46.530 --> 00:22:48.480 align:middle line:84%
