to have to marry you.

00:22:48.480 --> 00:22:50.680 align:middle line:84%
He wanted to marry this--
be with this other person.

00:22:50.680 --> 00:22:52.500 align:middle line:90%
>>SONI: Exactly.

00:22:52.500 --> 00:22:54.570 align:middle line:84%
That to me was
